    Main_CardAuthentication_Pcsc
    Handles the process of a Calypso card authentication using the PC/SC plugin and the Calypso Card Extension Service.

    Illustrates the loading of a key pair and Calypso certificates into a PKI card with SAM C1.

    Illustrates the loading of a key pair and Calypso certificates into a PKI card with SAM C1.
    Main_ChangePin_Pcsc
    Manages the process of changing the PIN code of a Calypso card using the PC/SC plugin, demonstrating both plain and encrypted PIN verification methods.
    Main_DataSigning_Pcsc
    Handles the execution of Calypso Legacy SAM data signing using an SAM resource service and the Legacy SAM extension service.
    Main_ExplicitSelectionAid_Pcsc
    Handles the process of explicit selection of a Calypso card using the PC/SC plugin, without implementing the observation of the reader.
    Main_ExplicitSelectionAid_Stub
    Handles the process of explicit selection of a Calypso card using the Stub plugin, without implementing the observation of the reader.
    Main_ExtendedModeSession_Pcsc
    Handles the process of a Calypso card in Extended Mode using the PC/SC plugin and the Calypso Card Extension Service.
    Main_MultipleSession_Pcsc
    Handles the process of executing multiple sessions on a Calypso card using the PC/SC plugin, particularly to bypass the card's modification buffer limitation.
